cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.MM 

The paper deals with machine learning and perceptual similarity modeling, which are core topics in the subfield of machine learning (cs.LG). The use of auxiliary information and the incorporation of active learning techniques suggest a focus on computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of natural language processing (cs.CL) and multimedia (cs.MM) in the evaluation of their approach, which further supports these sub-categories.
